"{\"uid\": \"newseu.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-08-The-oldest-Olympic-winner-s-lifelong-legacy-of-strength-and-resilience-1vR5rwAyRck-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pablo Gutierrez in Budapest  Copied  The world's oldest living Olympic champion, Agnes Keleti, remains a vibrant fan of the Games, cheering for athletes at every event in Paris.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 224, \"end\": 232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7342896949696872e-13, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}, {\"begin\": 286, \"end\": 298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c1gnes_Keleti\", \"score\": 0.9999997630584684, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Agnes Keleti\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c1gnes_Keleti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c1gnes_Keleti\"}, {\"begin\": 376, \"end\": 381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998071871, \"rank\": 1.9295542924575442e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At 103 years old, Keleti's enduring spirit and inspiring life story continue to captivate new generations.\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 490, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Each gleaming trophy and medal she earned represents a moment of glory and countless hours of dedication.\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 596, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sports offered me lifelong benefits that extended far beyond just the game itself,\\\" says Keleti.\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 695, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Keleti is not only the world's oldest living Olympic champion but also Hungary's greatest Olympic gymnast, with a remarkable total of 10 medals, including five gold.\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 862, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 768, \"end\": 775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.9999989900903171, \"rank\": 5.2375157458712e-07, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She is a symbol of the Olympian ethic and the idea that sportsmen and women can become models for many people to follow,\\\" says Samu Szemerey, curator of the Olympic Exhibit in Budapest.\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 1050, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 888, \"end\": 896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999997352588603, \"rank\": 2.6474040075237463e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 992, \"end\": 996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/As-Samu\", \"score\": 0.9999999195215455, \"rank\": 8.045972196013805e-08, \"text\": \"Samu\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/As-Samu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/As-Samu\"}, {\"begin\": 1041, \"end\": 1049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7342896949696872e-13, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Being born in 1921 meant Keleti would lose many of her prime years to World War II, but being born Jewish meant the potential for much bigger danger.\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The war forced her into hiding \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093\\u00a0her father and other relatives were killed at Auschwitz.\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1293, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1283, \"end\": 1292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auschwitz_concentration_camp\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.04523991381581e-14, \"text\": \"Auschwitz\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auschwitz_concentration_camp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auschwitz_concentration_camp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the war, Keleti returned to competition, but injury ruled her out of the 1948 Olympics in London.\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1391, \"end\": 1397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999977253538, \"rank\": 1.269837923397377e-09, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it was at the 1952 Olympics in Helsinki \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 which had been due to host the 1940 Games and was still healing from its own war wounds \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 that she made her mark.\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1433, \"end\": 1441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helsinki\", \"score\": 0.9999999999895408, \"rank\": 1.0339150466818914e-11, \"text\": \"Helsinki\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helsinki\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helsinki\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although already in her thirties, Keleti dazzled the audience in Helsinki and beyond with her performances.\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1670, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1628, \"end\": 1636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helsinki\", \"score\": 0.9999999999895408, \"rank\": 1.0339150466818914e-11, \"text\": \"Helsinki\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helsinki\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Helsinki\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She won gold for floor exercise, silver in the team all-round event, and two bronzes \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 on the uneven bars and in the team portable apparatus event.\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1820, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Three more medals at the 1954 World Championships in Rome set her up for the 1956 Melbourne Olympics, and Keleti seized her chance for greater visibility.\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1875, \"end\": 1879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\", \"score\": 0.9497330757667818, \"rank\": 0.05273586422612556, \"text\": \"Rome\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\"}, {\"begin\": 1899, \"end\": 1922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1956_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.190062465795006e-22, \"text\": \"1956 Melbourne Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1956_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1956_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1904, \"end\": 1922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1956_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Melbourne Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1956_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1956_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With her performances broadcast on television to a growing global audience, she left a lasting impact on world gymnastics.\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 2099, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE  Palestinian Olympians pursue peace in Paris  The Olympics' fastest sport  Olympics boxing achieves gender equality  In all, she won six medals in Melbourne \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 four gold and two silver.\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2297, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2112, \"end\": 2123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"score\": 0.9475729593014259, \"rank\": 0.055246886426189336, \"text\": \"Palestinian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\"}, {\"begin\": 2150, \"end\": 2155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998071871, \"rank\": 1.9295542924575442e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2258, \"end\": 2267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9999842693974093, \"rank\": 1.5728525087410157e-05, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She retained her gold in floor exercise, upgraded her two 1952 bronzes in uneven bars and team portable to golds, and added the balance beam.\", \"from\": 2298, \"to\": 2439, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The silvers came in the individual and team all-around events.\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2502, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not bad for a 35-year-old war survivor.\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2542, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No wonder that Keleti's name still shines today in Budapest, alongside other Olympians who have inspired millions.\", \"from\": 2544, \"to\": 2658, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2595, \"end\": 2603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7342896949696872e-13, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Nations gather around sports, especially the Olympics, as a space where this kind of togetherness and fair completions are the most important things,\\\" Szemerey notes.\", \"from\": 2660, \"to\": 2827, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As Keleti watches the Games, she takes a moment to remind us of the Olympics' greater purpose: uniting people, especially during global turmoil.\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2973, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When the world unites for the Olympics, Keleti says it sends a powerful message - together, we are stronger against darkness.\", \"from\": 2974, \"to\": 3099, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This generation of athletes, she believes, has the power to help bring light to the world.\", \"from\": 3100, \"to\": 3190, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, as Team Hungary progresses through each Olympic event, Keleti and her son show their support.\", \"from\": 3192, \"to\": 3296, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3206, \"end\": 3218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Team Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Compared to the size of the country, they excel in a lot of sports, and I hope they come back with lots of medals,\\\" says Raphael Keleti, \\u00c3\\u0081gnes Keleti's son.\", \"from\": 3298, \"to\": 3456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3420, \"end\": 3427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raphael\", \"score\": 0.9999999999931788, \"rank\": 6.797865047672141e-12, \"text\": \"Raphael\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raphael\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raphael\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Watching the Paris Olympics unfold, Keleti sees it as a testament to the enduring spirit of the Games - and their power to unite and inspire us all.\", \"from\": 3458, \"to\": 3606, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe toStoryboard: A weekly newsletterbringing you the best of CGTN every Friday  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 3608, \"to\": 3955, \"entities\": []}]}"